snippet.title: Microvision - Block Buster © 1979 Milton Bradley - Gameplay
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
A skill and action game that challenges your ability to react quickly. Break down the wall, block by block! Keep the ball smashing into the wall! Break through the third row & the pace picks up!
